Package se.itu.hunt

Class Position

  • java.lang.Object
    • se.itu.hunt.Position
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GridPosition, TablePosition

    public class Position
extends Object

    Represents a Position on a Board in this game. Uses a classic (x, y) representation for a coordinate.

    This class is immutable.
